  "text": "GST Pull-Down Assays. GST-tagged proteins were prepared as described [CITATION_1] . One microgram of GST-tagged proteins was immobilized to 20 μL of a 50% (vol/vol) glutathione-Agarose slurry (Pierce) at 4°C, overnight. After three washes, 100 ng of recombinant FLAG-Fox-1 (F:Fox-1) was incubated with immobilized GST-proteins at 4°C for 1 h. Reactions were washed three times and analyzed by immunoblotting.",
